            "Adjusted": "Case en: Ten with optional label fen; }; } Tv; For example: an enumerated type VariantTag with values apple(0) and orange(1); a structure V1 with a uint16 number and a variable-length opaque string of up to 10 bytes; a structure V2 with a uint32 number and a fixed-length opaque string of 10 bytes; a structure VariantRecord with a VariantTag type field and a select statement that chooses V1 for apple or V2 for orange based on VariantRecord.type."
