        {
            "Original": "These values refer solely to signatures which appear in certificates (see Section 4.4.2.2) and are not defined for use in signed TLS handshake messages, although they MAY appear in \"signature_algorithms\" and \"signature_algorithms_cert\" for backward compatibility with TLS 1.2.",
            "Adjusted": "The RSASSA-PKCS1-v1_5 algorithm values refer solely to signatures which appear in certificates and are not defined for use in signed TLS handshake messages, although they may appear in signature algorithm extensions for backward compatibility with TLS 1.2."
