        },
        {
            "Original": "Legacy algorithms: Indicates algorithms which are being deprecated because they use algorithms with known weaknesses, specifically SHA-1 which is used in this context with either (1) RSA using RSASSA-PKCS1-v1_5 or (2) ECDSA.",
