4. Handshake Protocol -> 4.4. Authentica:
{
    "4.4.4. Finished": [
        {
            "Original": "The Finished message is the final message in the Authentication Block.",
            "Adjusted": "No change"
        },
        {
            "Original": "It is essential for providing authentication of the handshake and of the computed keys.",
            "Adjusted": "The Finished message is essential for providing authentication of the handshake and of the computed keys."
