            "Adjusted": "In TLS 1.3, the verify_data is the size of the HMAC output for the Hash used for the handshake."
        },
        {
            "Original": "Note: Alerts and any other non-handshake record types are not handshake messages and are not included in the hash computations.",
            "Adjusted": "No change"
        },
        {
            "Original": "Any records following a Finished message MUST be encrypted under the appropriate application traffic key as described in Section 7.2.",
            "Adjusted": "No change"
